<h3 id="defecation-en">Defecation System (J key)</h3>
<p>The defecation meter fills from eating (cooked meat: +5, rotten flesh: +8, watermelon: +2, bread: +2). At 80, it triggers involuntarily (Nausea for 5 min + Slowness I for 1 min). Press <strong>J</strong> to defecate manually!</p>
